national committee sent press releases to the districts of 21 
democrats accusing them of supporting sexually explicit and 
antireligious works of art 
the nea is required by law to support materials that in the 
experts view foster excellence are reflective of exceptional 
talent and have significant literary scholarly cultural or 
artistic merit 
the 112 billion measure for the interior department cultural 
and other programs is for fiscal 1990 which began sunday 
the legislation also extends for another year a ban on the 
leasing of offshore tracts for oil and gas drilling imposes new 
restrictions on lobbyists who seek federal money for clients and 
allows lumber companies to cut timber on federally owned land in 
the northwest while protecting areas inhabited by the rare spotted 
owl 
