exemption for attorneys fees but he acknowledges the political 
climate makes it difficult for congress to appear as if somehow 
supporting drug dealers 
for now many lawyers say they will continue their criminal 
practice but the days of an elite group of top criminal attorneys 
may be numbered 
in the next couple of years you will see some of the best and 
the brightest leaving criminal practice quinon said people 
are already beginning to handle civil cases that was unthinkable a 
short while ago 
