children the capsules must be broken and smaller amounts of the 
foultasting medicine mixed with juice or another liquid 
the situation is absurd the company should file an application 
as soon as possible and develop a dosage that is appropriate for 
childern aids doesnt discriminate against children neither 
should burroughs 
