663 billion up 103 percent from 602 billion in 1987 the 
record was 73 billion in 1984 
the 17 billion for net income was up 13 percent from 15 
billion in 1987 and was almost twoandahalf times the 1986 level 
of 688 million last years net income was exceeded only by 19 
billion in 1980 and 18 billion in 1976 
