from ohio and the relatives heard her voice on the telephone 
earlier this week 
i feel better than i have in the last 10 months ms christ 
said after the three spent some time by themselves looking at 
family photographs i never broke down 
time will take care of everything ms white said we want 
her to come home but we want whats best for her 
ms ellish said she did not recognize ms christ and ms white 
but did not doubt they were her relatives 
i cant put this into focus it doesnt all register she 
said theres still that feeling of why dont i remember 
at the time of her disappearance ms ellish a telephone company 
computer analyst was having personal problems with her 18yearold 
daughter and was being treated for migraine headaches and stress 
her sister said she also has two sons ages 20 and 29 
ms ellish said doctors told her the memory loss was caused by a 
traumatic event and that her memory may return either gradually or 
in a flash 
