no intention to prevent fair competition 
the reason we cannot fix the machines is that many of the 
computers purchased through nonauthorized dealers do not have 
serial numbers which is the most important identification of apple 
products for repair she said 
while some individual importers have been reported erasing 
serial numbers to avoid tracing and interference with their supply 
sources steps fukutomi said his stores has been using the serial 
numbers since sept 1 ending the repair problem 
