thrifts 
so far the rtc has spent 20 billion 18 billion to close the 
24 small sampls 83 billion to handle five large institutions by 
next week and five smaller notyetcompleted deals 85 billion to 
replace highcost deposits and 14 billion as a reserve fund to 
handle liquidity problems at thrifts that have failed but are still 
open seidman said 
