district court 
belo has used its newspapertelevision combination to engage 
in conduct that severely undermines competition between the dallas 
morning news and the dallas times herald says the petition to 
the fcc 
the fcc has outlawed joint newspapertelevision ownership since 
1975 but allowed such ownership to continue in dallas and other 
cities where it already was in place 
wfaa is the leading television station in the dallasfort worth 
market 
